@correct_culture_primary_score = 100
@better_than_the_alternatives_score = 50
@always_primary_score = 1000
@never_primary_score = -1000

# special titles
k_papal_state = {			# Primas Britanniarum ("Primate/Primacy of the Britannias") for now
	color={ 200 200 165 }
	definite_form = yes
	ruler_uses_title_name = no
	can_use_nomadic_naming = no
	landless = yes

	capital = c_londinium		# Temporary

	ai_primary_priority = {
		add = @always_primary_score
	}

	destroy_if_invalid_heir = yes
	no_automatic_claims = yes
	always_follows_primary_heir = yes
	de_jure_drift_disabled = yes
}

								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_brythonic

		d_argoed = {	
			color={ 95 130 90 }
			
			capital = c_setantia
	
			de_jure_drift_disabled = yes
			can_be_named_after_dynasty = no
			
			can_create = {
				can_create_roman_celtic_titles_trigger = yes
			}
	
			ai_primary_priority = {
				if = {
					limit = {
						culture = { 
							OR = {
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_brythonic
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_latin
							}
						}
					}
					add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
				}
			}
			
			cultural_names = {
				name_list_briton = cn_argoed
				name_list_cumbrian = cn_argoed
				name_list_armorican = cn_argoed
				name_list_pictish = cn_argoed_pictish
				name_list_roman = cn_setantia

		d_selgovae = {	
			color={ 100 170 145 }
			
			capital = c_armterid
	
			de_jure_drift_disabled = yes
			can_be_named_after_dynasty = no
			
			can_create = {
				can_create_roman_celtic_titles_trigger = yes
			}
	
			ai_primary_priority = {
				if = {
					limit = {
						culture = { 
							OR = {
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_brythonic
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_latin
							}
						}
					}
					add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
				}
			}
			
			cultural_names = {
				name_list_roman = cn_selgovia
				name_list_romanogallic = cn_selgovia
				name_list_romanorhaetian = cn_selgovia
				name_list_romanoaquitanian = cn_selgovia
				name_list_romanogermanic = cn_selgovia
				name_list_romanoscandian = cn_selgovia

				name_list_armenian = cn_selgovia_greek
				name_list_romanosyrian = cn_selgovia_greek
				name_list_romanoegyptian = cn_selgovia_greek

	k_lothian = {          
		color={ 123 170 181 }
		
		capital = c_din_eidyn
	
		de_jure_drift_disabled = yes
		can_be_named_after_dynasty = no
		
		can_create = {
			can_create_briton_kingdom_trigger = yes
		}
		
		d_eidyn = {				
			color={ 100 150 156 }
			
			capital = c_din_eidyn
	
			de_jure_drift_disabled = yes
			can_be_named_after_dynasty = no
			
			can_create = {
				can_create_roman_celtic_titles_trigger = yes
			}
	
			ai_primary_priority = {
				if = {
					limit = {
						culture = { 
							OR = {
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_brythonic
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_latin
							}
						}
					}
					add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
				}
			}
			
			cultural_names = {
				name_list_roman = cn_votadinia
				name_list_romanogallic = cn_votadinia
				name_list_romanorhaetian = cn_votadinia
				name_list_romanoaquitanian = cn_votadinia
				name_list_romanogermanic = cn_votadinia
				name_list_romanoscandian = cn_votadinia
				name_list_romanonumidian = cn_votadinia
				name_list_romanoafrican = cn_votadinia

							}
						}
					}
					add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
				}
			}

			de_jure_drift_disabled = yes
			can_be_named_after_dynasty = no

				can_create_roman_celtic_titles_trigger = yes
			}
	
			ai_primary_priority = {
				if = {
					limit = {
						culture = { 
							OR = {
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_brythonic
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_latin
							}
						}
					}
					add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
				}
			}

	k_ynys_man = {
		color={ 130 170 80 }
		
		capital = c_german
	
		de_jure_drift_disabled = yes
		can_be_named_after_dynasty = no
		
		can_create = {
			can_create_briton_kingdom_trigger = yes
			highest_held_title_tier < tier_king
			has_primary_title = title:d_ynys_man
			realm_size >= 6
		}
			
		cultural_names = {
			name_list_roman = cn_monapia
			name_list_romanogallic = cn_monapia

			name_list_oldirish = cn_mannin_gaelic
			name_list_gaelic = cn_mannin_gaelic

			name_list_cumbrian = cn_manaw_brythonic
			name_list_armorican = cn_manaw_brythonic
			name_list_pictish = cn_manaw_pictish
		}
		
		d_ynys_man = {				
			color={ 130 170 80 }
			
			capital = c_german
	
			de_jure_drift_disabled = yes
			can_be_named_after_dynasty = no
			
			can_create = {
				can_create_roman_celtic_titles_trigger = yes
			}
	
			ai_primary_priority = {
				if = {
					limit = {
						culture = { 
							OR = {
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_brythonic
								has_cultural_pillar = heritage_latin
							}
						}
					}
					add = @better_than_the_alternatives_score
				}
			}
			
			cultural_names = {
				name_list_roman = cn_monapia
				name_list_romanogallic = cn_monapia
				name_list_romanorhaetian = cn_monapia
				name_list_romanoaquitanian = cn_monapia
				name_list_romanogermanic = cn_monapia
				name_list_romanoscandian = cn_monapia

		is_brythonic_culture_trigger = yes

				# TODO Need to make custom description for this...
				OR = {
					completely_controls = title:c_caer_gei
					completely_controls = title:c_dunoding
				}
			}
		}
	}
}
